main event: Two circular white objects, resembling satellites, were observed traveling from southeast to northwest for approximately 30 seconds.
interesting points: The objects were seen just before sunset., A shooting star was observed after the UFOs were no longer in view., Sound of jet noise was heard during the sighting but the jet was not in view., The duration of the sighting was around 20 to 30 seconds., The report includes a hand-drawn sketch of a plant, but no photographs of the sighting.
witness description: details of the observation from a single report
